To permannetly actiavte ot keep running hhtpd server in conatiner we have to give command 
# vim /root/.bashrc
Here you add commands

# rm -f /var/run/httpd/* --> To delete old httpd apache service files
# /usr/sbin/httpd  --> To start httpd apache server

These commands will on restart of container as  container always runs .bashrc on startup
